<L>__{int burning church night}
<A>__{ the third cardinal, still alive, is suspended over the searing flames. a word is branded into the center of his bared chest:}
<C>__{fire.}
<A>__{vatican police, led by olivetti and vincenzo, race into the building and draw their weapons. olivetti shouts to them in italian, looking for a way to cut down the agonized cardinal. langdon races toward the pyre, but is repelled by a wall of heat ten feet away. the cardinal screams, and langdon looks to the sides, following the cables that reach to the walls. one of the vatican cops ducks}
